data.description: Welcome to this charming home in the heart of Fairbanks, Alaska! This home has a cozy and inviting atmosphere, this delightful residence offers 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom,  a fully finished basement, and an oversized making it he perfect choice for you. When you walk inside you notice the improvements the owner has made to the house, featuring new flooring & remodeled bathroom. Plenty of natural light in this house, extra storage, brand new boiler. City maintained and paved roads. Finished basement makes home seem much larger than it is. Don't Miss the opportunity to make this charming Fairbanks residence your own.
